{"tid":1071521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【張超雄之詭辯】我哋邊個祖宗唔係抵壘政策時(即捕即解政策前)既偷渡難民","createTime":"2019-03-21T11:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T01:15:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"dda802d6cadedb11b4a313dced2746be763a2b1e","tid":1071521,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工黨議員張超雄則替新移民辯護，不滿有人嘲諷內地新移民為「蝗蟲」，掠奪港人資源，「呢個係明顯嘅歧視，我哋邊個祖宗唔係移民？」他又指，新移民多是弱勢、基層婦女，而這班人也是港人的家人，跨境婚姻也是以基層為主，而且新移民來港後，當中不少人擔任照顧者的角色：「嚟港控制、威脅我哋嘅政治、文化，並唔係呢批人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190321/59393431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F59393431&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3BD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=fd98ae8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F59393431&h=e560bf87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190321/59393431</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n張超雄將歷史史實簡化至詭辯程度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkmemory.hk/MHK/collections/public_housing/all_items/images/201307/W020130702795028468880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmemory.hk%2FMHK%2Fcollections%2Fpublic_housing%2Fall_items%2Fimages%2F201307%2FW020130702795028468880.jpg&h=6ebdb4ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【FACT CHECK】<br />\n(1) 上一代係由支那國因為飽受生命威脅, 偷渡黎香港既難民, 唔係一黎到就拿福利既「移民」<br />\n(2) 上一代黎到香港, 係自己搭木屋, 訓樓梯底, 唔係一黎即要排隊搶公屋要綜援既「移民」<br />\n(3) 上一代偷渡黎港, 係要游水偷渡, 係冒生命危險, 黎到既係壯年之人, 唔係愛滋肺癌一概不理, 一到即時去醫院洗腎既「移民」<br />\n(4) 上一代偷渡湧港, 完全只限「抵壘政策」時期既事，並唔係永久每日150人不變鐵律<br />\n(5) 「抵壘政策」係你有能力潛行進入市區, 避過軍警, 先會有身份證, 唔係賄賂公安拿單程證老奉<br />\n(6) 上一代偷渡湧港,  係即時令香港超負荷, 全社會各項設施即時飽和, 社會秩序接近崩潰邊緣, 香港英治政府係立即取消「抵壘政策」, 改為「即捕即解」"},{"pid":"0815317056623fe38a59dd3e6353247486e0fe77","tid":1071521,"uid":220701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"蝻亞老豆又想轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adfd7c01e5118fa7f8121be215d8e317e5246ea","tid":1071521,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建制派何君堯就以「新陳代謝」形容單程證制度，他認為香港人口增長在世界水平屬偏低，斥泛民「逼爆香港」言論危言聳聽，稱香港需要「換血」解決人口老化，批評言論挑起矛盾，籲「靜悄悄，做好事，積多啲陰德」。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053ca4c5236b6d808e22cedc62fa42c2d5e980ea","tid":1071521,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"以前義勇軍守邊境架<br />\n<br />\n不如依家重召義勇軍啦, 你班單程證能越過到義勇軍防線入到市區界限街以南, 比身份證你又點話?<br />\n<br />\n張超雄你試唔試？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20130326/large/fw12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20130326%2Flarge%2Ffw12.jpg&h=6f18b33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"494c2c02ff822558ea27e2e31e0bb9be53501cee","tid":1071521,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"我祖宗唔係"},{"pid":"a776fe91066082b048bf56d03bb540d5c2e9045e","tid":1071521,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"你不如話美國mark zuckerberg老婆都係新移民<br />\n以前果班咁勤力建設香港<br />\n而家果d好多都係黎佔用資源 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3225dde56475afeb0835cbb68b7ce2fbb9b0ca35","tid":1071521,"uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"有人常說，你們先來，你們的父母都是新移民，不應該排斥，否則你們很忘本。<br />\n<br />\n這種說法令人覺得很可笑，因為正如一架電梯根據消防條例，最多只能盛載12人，12人入去，有時不夠就10人，因為裡面有3人特別肥。一超過1600磅，就「咇咇」電梯門關不上。第13、14個走得慢想進來，對不起請你出去。<br />\n<br />\n走得慢的可否問電梯內的12個，為什麼你不出來？為什麼我不能進來？不是排斥你，不是歧視你，不是仇恨你，而是電梯就只有這麼大，這些三歲小孩都明白。"},{"pid":"2f5e15666c2833a5977709157616f1ce0809ec61","tid":1071521,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"張超雄死全家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3b876f777267b010f3c1aec6a8996b8b3a2ff8","tid":1071521,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"咁點睇外國移民政策咁撚難一家團聚"},{"pid":"83a1d10ef04b0cccf0f3f5c592d8e8bc938673b8","tid":1071521,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:59:06.000Z","msg":"大把香港原居民啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：長洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796b4e9c91cb41294300f9613df323c17039952f","tid":1071521,"uid":166040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"我唔係喎<br />\n大嶼山原居民"},{"pid":"f3967fc5039470e66cf58b2e5f0c3d040bc331ff","tid":1071521,"uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"我姓劉，祖宗姓獨孤<br />\n係鮮卑貴族"},{"pid":"758554d8daa0bc45a9760e3dc6f56cebd0314939","tid":1071521,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053ca4c5236b6d808e22cedc62fa42c2d5e980ea","tid":1071521,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"以前義勇軍守邊境架<br />\n<br />\n不如依家重召義勇軍啦, 你班單程證能越過到義勇軍防線入到市區界限街以南, 比身份證你又點話?<br />\n<br />\n張超雄你試唔試？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20130326/large/fw12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20130326%2Flarge%2Ffw12.jpg&h=6f18b33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"准唔准放狗同用槍掃?"},{"pid":"a55917b75e0ec9f16e8d94462d76bc19409cd0f7","tid":1071521,